name: Virtual Landscapes 01/20
description:
I am often amazed by the magnificent view of nature. As I dive into the 3D world, I am even more impressed by the uniqueness of every mountain, every hill, and even tree or grass. Thus, in this series, I try to create these 3D landscapes to tribute our breathtaking world. And these are the experiments of 3D realistic landscapes. 

Series: 01/20

(The first one of this series is kind of a special one, cause only this one is square size, the rest of the series come with 16:9)
